    "story_name": "莫尔提斯 第2话 美好又丑陋的世界",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "我说，伊莉雅。\\n我对莫尔提斯做了什么吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯？为什么这么问？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "就是，最近这段时间\\n总能感觉到莫尔提斯的视线……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这种事直接问他就好了嘛。\\n我说，莫尔提斯。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你为什么\\n总是盯着梅奈看啊？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "因为漂亮。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "诶！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "难道，你对梅奈……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "梅奈的翅膀、很漂亮。\\n想一直看。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "噢，是这么回事啊……吓我一跳。\\n我还以为你喜欢上梅奈了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "喜欢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我自言自语罢了。莫尔提斯，\\n你喜欢漂亮的东西吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "嗯。梅奈，能不能把翅膀\\n取下来让我仔细看看？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "什么……我、我的翅膀\\n是取不下来的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "是吗……伊莉雅，炼金术\\n能炼成精灵的翅膀吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "唔……炼成精灵的翅膀啊。\\n听起来有点意思。\\n梅奈，能让我研究下你的翅膀吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "我说伊莉雅，\\n你跟着说什么胡话呢！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "啊哈哈，抱歉抱歉。\\n我是开玩笑的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔提斯，除了精灵的翅膀，\\n还有很多漂亮的东西哦。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "真的吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯，我们一起去看吧。\\n大家，都跟我来！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "怎么样？这片湖很美吧？\\n这是我最喜欢的地方之一。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "来湖畔郊游，\\n这主意真不错。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "嗯，这里的确好美……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅，水还能\\n这么闪闪发亮吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这不是水本身在发光，\\n而是反射太阳的光。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "反射太阳的光……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "没错，光投到物质上\\n会反射到各个方向。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这片美丽的景色就是这样诞生的。\\n是不是很厉害？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "嗯！伊莉雅！\\n天上飞的那个也是精灵吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "天上？啊，那个不是精灵，\\n是一种叫鸟的生物。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "鸟？\\n鸟也会在天上飞吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "没错。鸟跟精灵一样也有翅膀，\\n能让它们在空中翱翔呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "真好啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "唔……我当时是不是应该\\n炼一个带翅膀的肉体呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "伊莉雅，为人父母\\n可不能过度溺爱孩子。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "呵呵……嗯？\\n魔力突然开始紊乱？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "这是……\\n大家，快趴下！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "还好……声音离得很远。\\n从只射了一发来看，\\n应该只是在试枪吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "吓了我一跳呢……\\n居然会在这种地方\\n进行军事训练……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅，\\n我们去声音的源头那里吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你突然之间怎么了？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我看见刚才那只鸟掉下去了！\\n得去救它才行！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你说什么！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "军方的人……已经走了吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "伊莉雅，为什么我们要藏起来？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "被军方发现的话会有麻烦。\\n我们还是快点找鸟吧。\\n你很担心它吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "嗯……\\n希望它没有受伤……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "啾……啾啾……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "这声音是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "等等！莫尔提斯！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "快看！我找到它了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "好重的伤……我这就给它治疗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这伤……果然是刚才的\\n军事训练导致的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "为什么……\\n军方要进行这种训练？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "因为，现在这个世界上，\\n人类正在和龙打仗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "打仗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "打仗……就是，互相残杀。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "互相残杀……\\n为什么、一定要做这种事？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "因为人类发达的文明\\n伤害到了龙。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "但人类并没有摒弃其文明，\\n而是选择了与龙开战。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这是赌上了各自\\n生死存亡的战争……\\n其影响正在不断扩大。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "等等。照你刚才所说的，\\n打仗的不是人类和龙吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "那为什么毫无关系的鸟\\n要受这么重的伤？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "莫尔提斯，\\n打仗就是这样的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "只要开始打仗，\\n就会有无辜的人遭殃。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "就连眼前这片美丽的景色\\n也会消失在战火之中吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "这……这也、\\n太过分了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯，是很过分。\\n但这就是发生在\\n这个世界的丑陋现实。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "很可惜，这个世界上\\n并不全是漂亮的东西。\\n这真的让人厌恶。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "伊莉雅，莫尔提斯！\\n鸟的伤治好了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "真的吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120030_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "鸟",
            "context": "啾……啾啾！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "呵呵，太好了，它又有精神了呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "塞西娅，谢谢你。\\n它能恢复真是太好了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "这个世界上……\\n并不全是漂亮的东西……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}